{"stage":"facts","title":"Kikitori レイテンシ最適化","goalSlug":"latency-optimization","facts":[{"id":"fact-1","text":"エンドツーエンド遅延（録音終了→ペースト完了）を50ms以下に短縮する","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":false,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":false},{"id":"fact-2","text":"apple_speech 音声認識エンジンを最優先で最適化する","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":false,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":false},{"id":"fact-3","text":"逐次処理（録音→認識→ペースト）のまま各段階の無駄を削る。パイプライン化は今回スコープ外","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":false,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":false},{"id":"fact-4","text":"録音開始の応答速度（ホットキー押下→録音開始）を改善する","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":true,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":true},{"id":"fact-5","text":"音声認識エンジン（apple_speech）の処理速度を改善する","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":true,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":true},{"id":"fact-6","text":"ペースト処理（クリップボード+Cmd+V）の遅延を改善する","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":true,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":true},{"id":"fact-7","text":"各段階の遅延を計測するインフラを整備する（プロファイリングログ、ベンチマーク）","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":true,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":true},{"id":"fact-8","text":"mlx-whisper の最適化は今回スコープ外（apple_speech 優先のため）","accepted":true,"removed":false,"automatedVerification":false,"recommendedAutomatedVerification":false}]}
